## DnaHoloHashMap class

A Map of DnaHash to HoloHashMap.

i.e. A Map of DnaHash to a Map of HoloHash to a value.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare class DnaHoloHashMap<K extends HoloHash, T> 
```
